fields.description:
Raised this improvement ticket in regards to customer's suggestion to have POM in our Elastic Image distribution files.

{quote}
When I'm building the AMI to be used by elastic bamboo agents I actually use Maven to get the needed binaries to be then put on the image, so the POM is actually rather convenient to have.

And, given that you use Maven (hence the POM), it's also a good indicator for me whether the release was created properly. This helps me to at least get some baseline indication whether I should use that version in absence of any other information.

I want to be able to produce all parts of our software automatically, including the images used by Bamboo, based on information checked into our version control system.
{quote}

h2. Resource
Created the following JAR just to test the issue:
{code:java|title=EnvMap.java}
import java.util.Map;

public class EnvMap {
    public static void main (String[] args) {
        Map<String, String> env = System.getenv();
        for (String envName : env.keySet()) {
            System.out.format("%s=%s%n",
                              envName,
                              env.get(envName));
        }
    }
}
{code}
{noformat}
# Compile the Class
javac EnvMap.java

# Create manifest
echo "Main-Class: EnvMap" > manifest.txt

# Create JAR
jar cvfm EnvMap.jar manifest.txt *.class
{noformat}

h2. Replicate issue
Used the "{{EnvMap.jar}}" above created in the "{{Post Build Commands}}" as per following:
|*Failed Command*|java -jar /path/to/EnvMap.jar|
|*Environment Variables*|JAVA_OPTS="-Dgrape.root=/opt/grape-repo"|
In the build log I can find the same as you have suggested in the ticket.
{noformat}
build	01-Oct-2015 14:32:08	JAVA_OPTS=-Dgrape.root
{noformat}

h2. Issue
As you can notice from build result above, "{{JAVA_OPTS}}" properties has not been populated correctly

h2. Workaround
Running the same by removing the "{{JAVA_OPTS}}" provides the following output:
|*Environment Variables*|-Dgrape.root=/opt/grape-repo|
{noformat}
build	01-Oct-2015 14:36:56	JAVA_OPTS=-XX:MaxPermSize=256m -Xms256m -Xmx384m    
build	01-Oct-2015 14:36:56	grape.root=/opt/grape-repo
{noformat}

h3. Summary
Manually running Stages with different users create incorrect Stage's metadata

h3. Steps to Reproduce
